{"tid":2179614,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲覺得無啦啦特登走去學日文真係好毒(識日文勿入)","createTime":"2020-08-29T08:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T12:15:00.000Z","uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ea530757a4cab47f100cc6293c8ed9be7ad5fe29","tid":2179614,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"我自己公司有個肥肥地嘅女仔，成日講講下廣東話冇啦啦彈幾隻日文出嚟，咩好殘念...本當...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好奇問下佢點解識日文，佢答我自學，聽完真係差啲忍唔住笑出嚟，講講下廣東話彈句法文就話好型好優雅姐，冇啦啦講日文我以為佢搞緊笑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(當然我冇當面笑9佢，食lunch先同啲部門同事講起)<br />\n<br />\nNative呢種本身識就唔計啦，母語冇得選擇，但呢幾年成日啲KOL開始用識日文做其中一個賣點就覺得好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究工程嘢學德文、通商學西文，再唔係就俄文法文呢啲大宗多人用嘅實用語言，反而日文就真係得日本人識，除咗啲台灣廢老(通常冇權冇勢)，邊鬼個用日文同你交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd894a629e90232c44e005e1ab6752fa34ae07e","tid":2179614,"uid":222140,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"學多樣嘢冇壞 <br />\n最重要知道學嚟做咩 <br />\n用啲人學少少日文<br />\n用嚟睇咸網，網購，或者去旅行用<br />\n齋睇得明係最易<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6bf2b138e9ad8a51e485b7b3a4f0cdc6bf6ff0","tid":2179614,"uid":236359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"五毛風紀午安<br />\nbtw日文對廣東話黎講易學 日本市場又大 同埋唔使靠大陸"},{"pid":"d616ece3b3359d663e75dafc7c9e83ae59af2442","tid":2179614,"uid":155371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"咁都好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b8645d4d5f6c405a869926e080b76300201c92","tid":2179614,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬識日文"},{"pid":"9f9f524c3ecef0fc7c3372cd20927123d9b573a1","tid":2179614,"uid":49057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:54:48.000Z","msg":"同啲港女話唔記得中文淨係識英文一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係識一種語言根本就唔需要撈埋其它語言一齊講，要用其它語言代即係中文唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3316dca0b81c563c6af228042acff5b53e60f06e","tid":2179614,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6bf2b138e9ad8a51e485b7b3a4f0cdc6bf6ff0","tid":2179614,"uid":236359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"五毛風紀午安<br />\nbtw日文對廣東話黎講易學 日本市場又大 同埋唔使靠大陸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"想問下日本唔使靠大陸咁安倍點解唔封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fc76c9c88ef1acdbc0e0927ef8220b2fb497a8","tid":2179614,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"35b8645d4d5f6c405a869926e080b76300201c92","tid":2179614,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬識日文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:55:17.000Z","msg":"喂你唔好搞串個party喎"},{"pid":"729990ac50e17704a720ea53526247a4d410b024","tid":2179614,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b8645d4d5f6c405a869926e080b76300201c92","tid":2179614,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬識日文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034e757b8e5edf7dad3314f63f53ea104ab3fe1f","tid":2179614,"uid":263618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:56:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f814da43673970a35f94931a4a73e57c1197d1f4","tid":2179614,"ui